    "body": "I'm not quitesure what you mean by \"having readline\". The library we use for text edition is codemirror and support a lot of [keymaps](https://codemirror.net/doc/manual.html#keymaps) including vi, emacs shortcut, undo, redo, and extension for killring, and is even more feature rich; highlighting, multicursor, etc... \n\nWhat more do you want ?\n\n(note that I don't see any difference in your demo than in any other texarea) \n"
